# Web Scraping

## Crawl4AI (preferred for new projects)
- Async-first web scraping
- Built-in LLM extraction
- Use with Playwright backend

## Playwright
- Use for dynamic JavaScript-heavy pages
- Headless mode for production
- Handle anti-bot detection

## Selenium
- Legacy scraper support
- Use WebDriverWait for dynamic content
- Chrome/Chromium in headless mode

## Best Practices
- Respect robots.txt
- Implement rate limiting and delays
- Handle retries with exponential backoff
- Store raw HTML for debugging
